  <h2>Third-Party Cookies</h2>
  <p>We do not use third-party advertising cookies. We do not use Facebook Pixel, Google Ads, or any retargeting technology. If we add analytics in the future, it will only activate with your explicit consent.</p>

  <h2>Managing Your Preferences</h2>
  <p>You can change your cookie preferences at any time by clearing your browser's local storage for 3d3d.ca, which will re-display the consent banner on your next visit. You can also disable cookies entirely through your browser settings, though this may affect site functionality.</p>

  <h2>Quebec Residents (Law 25)</h2>
  <p>Under Quebec's Law 25 (Act respecting the protection of personal information in the private sector), you have the right to refuse non-essential cookies. Our consent banner provides clear opt-in controls that comply with Law 25 requirements. Only necessary cookies are placed without consent.</p>

  <h2>PIPEDA Compliance</h2>
  <p>This cookie policy is provided in accordance with PIPEDA Principle 8 (Openness). Our use of cookies is limited to the purposes described above per Principle 4 (Limiting Collection). For privacy inquiries: <a href="mailto:info@3d3d.ca">info@3d3d.ca</a>.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Privacy Officer: <a href="mailto:info@3d3d.ca">info@3d3d.ca</a> · 3D3D Atlantic Cooperative, Fredericton, NB, Canada.</p>
